price: Namootas garee gareedhaan diinii Rabbii keessa kan seenan argite,
arabic: وَرَأَيۡتَ ٱلنَّاسَ يَدۡخُلُونَ فِي دِينِ ٱللَّهِ أَفۡوَاجٗا

version.title: Oromo translation
